<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A more straightforward sort of <a href=3D"http=
s://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31975621.257407/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc=
2VjLmdvdi9uZXdzL3ByZXNzLXJlbGVhc2UvMjAyMy0xMjM/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB73e=
dfd4a" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background=
-color: #ccc;"> Covid-driven insider trading</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Securities and Exchange Commission [Thursd=
ay] announced insider trading charges against Amit Dagar, a former Pfizer I=
nc. employee, and his close friend and business partner, Atul Bhiwapurkar, =
for trading in advance of the company=E2=80=99s November 5, 2021, announcem=
ent that a randomized, double-blind study of its COVID-19 antiviral treatme=
nt, Paxlovid, was successful. Following that announcement in which Pfizer=
=E2=80=99s CEO referred to the news as a =E2=80=9Cgame-changer=E2=80=9D in =
the global efforts to =E2=80=9Chalt the devastation=E2=80=9D of the pandemi=
c, the company=E2=80=99s stock price increased by nearly 11 percent, the la=
rgest single-day price move in the stock since 2009.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">According to the SEC=E2=80=99s complaint, Daga=
r was a senior statistical program lead for the Paxlovid drug trial, which =
began in July 2021 as part of the company=E2=80=99s efforts to address the =
global health pandemic. On the day before the Paxlovid announcement, the co=
mplaint alleges, Dagar learned material, nonpublic information about the su=
ccess of the trial. Specifically, the SEC alleges that Dagar=E2=80=99s supe=
rvisor informed him via chat that =E2=80=9Cwe got the outcome,=E2=80=9D the=
re was a =E2=80=9Clot of work lined up,=E2=80=9D and that there would be a =
=E2=80=9Cpress release tomorrow,=E2=80=9D to which Dagar responded with =E2=
=80=9Coh really=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Ckind of exciting.=E2=80=9D Several ho=
urs after that exchange, Dagar allegedly purchased short term, out-of-the-m=
oney Pfizer call options, including options that expired the very next day,=
 and then tipped Bhiwapurkar, who also purchased similar call options in Pf=
izer. The complaint alleges that Dagar=E2=80=99s and Bhiwapurkar=E2=80=99s =
trading generated approximately $214,395 and $60,300 respectively in illici=
t profits, which amounted to one-day investment returns of 2,458 percent an=
d 791 percent.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The case originated from the SEC=E2=80=99s Mar=
ket Abuse Unit=E2=80=99s Analysis and Detection Center, which uses data ana=
lysis tools to detect suspicious trading patterns.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CAs alleged in our complaint, Amit Dag=
ar misused his access to confidential clinical trial results to enrich hims=
elf and his friend, Atul Bhiwapurkar,=E2=80=9D said Joseph Sansone, Chief o=
f the Market Abuse Unit. =E2=80=9CDagar and Bhiwapurkar allegedly leveraged=
 this information by trading out-of-the-money call options to generate mass=
ive one-day returns. Thanks to our surveillance, the defendants must now fa=
ce the consequences of their greed.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There are also <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/31975621.257407/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuanVzdGljZS5nb3Yvd=
XNhby1zZG55L3ByL3VzLWF0dG9ybmV5LWFubm91bmNlcy1jaGFyZ2VzLWZvdXItc2VwYXJhdGUt=
aW5zaWRlci10cmFkaW5nLWNhc2VzLWFnYWluc3QtMTA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC3b1e10=
de" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">criminal charges</a>. Always the call options.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But come on! This was not some random financia=
l windfall for Pfizer; this was a=C2=A0<em>Covid treatment</em>. Be a littl=
e more creative! On Nov. 5, 2021, Pfizer announced this trial result and it=
s stock went up 11%. That day, Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd.=E2=80=99s stock=
 was up 8%. Carnival Corp. was up 9%.=C2=A0Delta Air Lines Inc. was up 8%. =
Wynn Resorts Ltd. was up 6%. Zoom Video Communications Inc. was down 6%. =
=E2=80=9CA game-changing Covid treatment will be good for the stocks of cru=
ise-ship companies, airlines and casinos and bad for work-from-home stocks=
=E2=80=9D was about as obvious a thesis as =E2=80=9Ca game-changing Covid t=
reatment will be good for the stock of the company that discovers it=E2=80=
