00; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> software and serv=
ers teams</a>, is gonna be in so much trouble when his boss, Twitter CEO Li=
nda Yaccarino, gets to the office today.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh I kid, I kid, but what a weird job that mus=
t be. The CEO job I mean. The software-and-servers job isn=E2=80=99t that w=
eird =E2=80=94=C2=A0<em>he=E2=80=99s in charge of a website=C2=A0</em>=E2=
=80=94 but he manages to make it weird.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As the ramification of Musk=E2=80=99s data bat=
tle became clear Saturday, some users complained about being limited.=C2=A0=
</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One user tweeted: =E2=80=9CYour addiction is a=
bout to be broken. We will all be free. See you guys at the park.=E2=80=9D=
=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CTouch grass again,=E2=80=9D Musk twee=
ted in reply.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ha ha ha! <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/31975621.257407/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9tYXR0X2xldm=
