 border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color=
: #ccc;"> Yes</a>! Musk is limiting access to Twitter in order to break its=
 users=E2=80=99 addiction and free them to touch grass.=C2=A0He has correct=
ly diagnosed the problem (Twitter users are too obsessed with it)=C2=A0and =
implemented a solution (don=E2=80=99t let them see too many tweets). Of cou=
rse to do this <em>he </em>had to become completely obsessed with Twitter, =
devote himself full-time to running it, tweet constantly and sink tens of b=
illions of dollars of his own money into buying Twitter and then breaking i=
t. He has sacrificed so much himself so that people like me can spend a bit=
 less time on Twitter; he has taken the burden of Twitter addiction from mi=
llions of users and put it all on himself. Thanks!</p>
