<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[2] In particular, in that case (Panuwat), the=
 defendant worked at a company with an insider-trading policy that specific=
ally forbade him from trading in competitors=E2=80=99 stock, and the SEC re=
ferenced that policy to argue that Panuwat was illegally misappropriating t=
he information to do his trades. Here, the SEC <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31975621.257407/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9saX=
