"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-=
bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid=
; background-color: #ccc;"> cites Pfizer=E2=80=99s Code of Conduct</a>, whi=
ch says =E2=80=9CSecurities laws and Pfizer policy prohibit us from disclos=
ing or using any material non-public or =E2=80=98inside=E2=80=99 informatio=
n that we acquire during our employment at Pfizer. We do not use material, =
non-public information to buy or sell the securities of Pfizer . . . before=
 this information is known publicly.=E2=80=9D This is not as clear a prohib=
ition on shadow trading.</p>
</div>
